&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Soloing and get two mobs?&amp;nbsp; Pet park one, move the mob to be close by your pet where you are both able to attack one, but you're not being attacked by two, and get your pet on the one you want killed.&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
